<div data-c-margin="top(double)">
    <h4 data-c-colour="c2" data-c-font-size="h4" data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Recommended Work Environment Skills</h4>
    <p data-c-margin="bottom(normal)">Before you begin to select your skill criteria for this job poster, we've analysed your work environment information and provided a few suggestions of skills you might want this candidate to have. You can view these skills in the "Work Environment" section below. These skills are optional, and you can use the + button to add them to your poster.</p>
    <div data-c-accordion="group">
        <div
            data-c-accordion="accordion"
            data-c-background="white(100)"
            data-c-border="right(thin, solid, black) left(thin, solid, black)">
            <button
                data-c-background="white(100)"
                aria-expanded="false"
                data-c-accordion="trigger"
                data-c-padding="right(triple)"
                tabindex="0"
                type="button">
                <div data-c-padding="top(normal) right bottom(normal) left(normal)">
                    <p data-c-font-size="h5" data-c-colour="c2" data-c-font-weight="bold">
                        Work Environment
                    </p>
                    <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="top(quarter)" data-c-font-size="h5">
                        1 Skill Selected
                    </p>
                </div>
                <span data-c-visibility="invisible">
                    Click to view...
                </span>
                <i
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    class="fas fa-plus"
                    data-c-accordion="icon--add">
                </i>
                <i
                    aria-hidden="true"
                    class="fas fa-minus"
                    data-c-accordion="icon--remove">
                </i>
            </button>
            <div
                aria-hidden="true"
                data-c-accordion="content">
                <div>
                    <p data-c-background="grey(10)" data-c-padding="all(normal)">Based on your work environment, we're suggesting the following skills. Use the + button to add a skill to your job poster, the pencil button to edit a skill, and the trash icon to remove it from your job poster.</p>
                    <div class="active job-builder-work-env-skill" data-c-padding="all(normal)">
                        <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(3of6) ds(5of8)">
                                <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Judgement</p>
                                <p class="level" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Strongly in Evidence</p>
                                <p>Defined as: Ability to make considered decisions and come to sensible conclusions that respect the perspectives of all parties involved.</p>
                                <div data-c-margin="top(normal)" data-c-tag="c1" data-c-font-size="small">Also selected in 2 other tasks (Tasks 1, 5).</div>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <button type="button">
                                    <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <button class="delete" type="button">
                                    <i data-c-colour="stop" class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button class="add" type="button">
                                    <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="job-builder-work-env-skill" data-c-padding="all(normal)">
                        <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(3of6) ds(5of8)">
                                <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Integrity</p>
                                <p class="level" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Asset</p>
                                <p>Defined as: Treating all those in the work environment with fairness, courtesy and respect for differences; performing the job in a manner that upholds the public trust and values co-workers.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <button type="button" >
                                    <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                                <button type="button" class="delete">
                                    <i data-c-colour="stop" class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" class="add">
                                    <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
